+pimg(project.folder, 'Process_UserFlow.png')

.copy The interaction design on the Fuelband was designed to inspire wearers to be active by rewarding them with motivational messages and a running tally of their fuel points running across a delightful dead-front display and fuel gauge.

+pimg(project.folder, 'nikefuelband-limited-edition-gold_edit2.png')

.copy One of the earliest expressions of the quantified self movement, we designed the Nike+ Fuelband to have refined, unisex aesthetic that made it one of the first wearables to be both fashionable and funcitonal.  Expanded editions included Fuelbands made with gold, silver, and a range of active colors.

